data.description: Gorgeous 5 bedroom, 4 bath home in Woodstock. Formal Dining Room with Butler's Pantry, 2 Story Fireside Family Room - Open to Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Island and Sun-Filled Breakfast Area. New Floors! Great Home Office with French Doors. Upper Level Features Owner's Suite with Walk-in Closet, Private Bath Offering Double Vanity, Garden Tub and Separate Shower. 3 Additional Bedrooms on the Upper Level with Walk-in Closets. Finished Basement Includes Rec Room, Wet Bar, Media Area, 5th Bedroom and Full Bath. New Deck Overlooks Level, Private Backyard. Great Corner Lot. New Roof. Don't Miss Out On This Amazing Home-This One Will Go Fast.
